  "description": "Newer (2013) West of Trail pool home for rent in Sarasota's historic Granada neighborhood — 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, 2,131 sq ft, private saltwater pool, Southside Elementary district. $5,500/month with pool care, lawn care and internet included; available August, furnished or unfurnished.",
